title: Didn't get my 10 year anniversary gift
body: So I already had Riot Kayle and I only received the icon in the mystery gift, didn't get any other things as the announcement said. Please help!

replies.body: The gifts are being sent out individually, so you may not get everything all at once.  We're still sending out gifts per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-), so we're not done just yet!  Hang on until this is all wrapped up, and the goods will come!
